Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:38.01,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,原创字幕: 人人影视\NYYeTs.com\N时间轴：wsr
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:38.91,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你回来了\NYou're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:42.37,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,想给你看看你做的好事...\NWanted to show you what you've done...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:45.19,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,并亲自感谢你\N...and to thank you in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.41,0:00:49.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这就是你做的\NYou did this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,看看我\NLook at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:52.47,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,亚蕾克西  看看你做了什么\NLexi, look what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:10.34,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(200,230)}陨落星辰\N第四季 第十集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:21.36,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,他在干嘛  接生吗\NWhat's he doing -- delivering a baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:22.75,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,既然知道怎么开车\NWell, we learned how to start the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:24.77,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,现在就要搞清楚怎么发动这玩意儿\NNow we got to figure out how to drive the damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.19,0:01:26.87,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,算了吧\NAh, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:29.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们一直在这飞船上找转向装置\NBeen looking all over this damn ship for the steering mechanism.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.63,0:01:31.11,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,连横舵柄都找不到\NCan't even find the damn yoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:32.59,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,也许根本没有\NPerhaps there isn't one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.62,0:01:36.50,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,激光飞船是靠无线电波远程控制的\NWe know that Beamers are remote controlled by radio waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:37.61,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这种是无人机\NThey're drones.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:40.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们得想办法超越远程控制\NWe must somehow override the remote control
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:42.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,对导航系统进行内部控制\Nand take local dominion of the navigation system.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:44.83,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没有横舵柄和方向盘  我们要怎么做\NHow do we do that if there's no yoke, no steering wheel?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.61,0:01:47.83,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,跟我来  我给你们看一样东西\NCome. Allow me to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:53.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,别乱动  很危险\NHey, don't touch anything. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:54.31,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你们也动了啊\NYou guys are touching stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:56.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们要搞明白怎么驾驶它\NWell, we're trying to figure out how to fly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:01:57.17,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我也是\NSo am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:02.87,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你什么时候进入的青少年叛逆期\NWhen did you enter your teenage rebellion phase?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.23,0:02:04.69,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,当我成为青少年的时候\NWhen I became a teenager.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:07.16,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这艘飞船把我的手臂刺得好疼\NThis ship stung the crap out of my arm, and it hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:09.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我只是想给你点建议\NI'm just trying to give you a little bit of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.55,0:02:10.67,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不需要建议\NI don't need advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:12.48,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好吧  那我就不啰嗦了\NOkay. Good talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.19,0:02:22.29,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,要我看什么\NWhat am I looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:23.68,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,找到月亮\NFind the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:25.82,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,往下5度再看\NLook 5 degrees below it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:31.29,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,一队激光飞船\NA whole line of Beamers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:33.79,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,它们在跟随归航信标飞向艾士芬尼基地\NThey are following the homing beacon to the Espheni base.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:36.91,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,也许我可以用替代通讯器\NPerhaps I can use the sub communicator
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:39.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,来模仿艾士芬尼的归航信标\Nto mimic the Espheni homing beacon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:41.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,欺骗这艘飞船  让它自行飞向月球\Nand trick the ship into flying to the moon on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.72,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你觉得你可以黑入无人机\NYou think you can hack into the drone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.73,0:02:44.49,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,然后让它起飞吗\Nand just go along for the ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:47.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-甚至都没必要找到方向盘  -正是\N- We don't even need to find the steering wheel. - Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:48.51,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你可以黑进去吗\NYou think you can hack into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:50.09,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,沃尔姆以前\NThe Volm have infiltrated
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:52.79,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就侵入并控制过艾士芬尼自动飞船\Nand taken control of automated Espheni ships before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:54.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我觉得可能性约百分之三十\NI will give it one chance in three.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:56.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:48.31,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,马特呢  他肯定又进去了\NWhere's Matt? He must've gone back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:49.84,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果他还活着  我要杀了他\NIf he's still alive, I'm gonna kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:51.52,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,他才13岁\NHey, he's 13 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:54.94,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们也会做同样的事  别对他太苛刻\NRemember, we would've done the same thing. Go easy on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:59.16,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不是告诉过你什么也别碰\NHey! I thought I told you not to touch anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:00.67,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你为什么总是怒气冲冲的\NWhy do you have to always be so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:02.37,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我想明白了\NLook. I figured something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.04,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,怎么了  马特  你做了什么\NWhat is this, Matt? What'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:05.26,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,推动了楼梯下的一个灯\NPushed one of the lights under the stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:06.55,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,舱口就打开了\Nand the hatch popped open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.17,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你碰了哪根触须之后飞船动了\NWhich tendrils did you touch to make the ship move?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:09.98,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,看着\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这根还有那根\NThis one and that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:14.32,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-你拉了这根  然后飞船就动了  -是啊\N- You pull this, and the wings move? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:16.89,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,拉吧\NPitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:19.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,偏航肯定在附近  这两个控制是整合在一起的\NYaw must be nearby. The two controls are integrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.34,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧  触须都集中在这一段了\NSee how the tendrils come together at the trunk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:23.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,看见了吗  爸爸  现在我们知道如何控制飞船了\NSee, dad? Now we know how to control pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:26.47,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,有时候艾士芬尼\NSometimes the Espheni
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:29.48,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,把它们的联络通道隐藏在地面光谱中\Ntry to hide their communication channels in the terrestrial spectrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:30.29,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是啊\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:33.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,等等  那是什么\NWait. What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:34.79,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,大家都听到了吗\NEverybody hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.15,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你们听到了吗  后退\NDid you guys hear that? Go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:44.45,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那是西班牙语吗\NIs that Spanish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:47.32,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-说西班牙语  -安东尼  他在说什么\N- Hablo Espanol. - Anthony, what's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:59.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,宇宙中最普遍的力量是什么\NWhat is the most pervasive force in the universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:03.31,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,引力  一个物体对另一个物体的吸引力\NGravity -- the attraction of a body to another body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:06.35,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就是引力让行星围绕太阳旋转\NIt's what makes the planets go around the suns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:13.09,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,宇宙也是同理\NIt's what makes the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:15.77,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你天生就有独特的能力\NAnd you have been born with the unique ability
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:19.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,能使用并控制引力和其它自然力量\Nto use gravity and other natural forces, to control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:22.99,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,开发你的潜力  你就能做出了不起的事\NAs you develop your power, you will do amazing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:25.42,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你看见远处的那些树吗\NDo you see those trees in the distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:26.70,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那颗高高的树\NThe tall one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:27.96,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那颗大橡树\NThe big, live oak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.04,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我想让你打破引力\NI want you to break the chains of graviy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.46,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,并将其结合在一起\Nthat hold it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:33.09,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不想毁掉它\NI don't want to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:34.60,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这不是毁掉它\NYou aren't destroying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:38.69,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,而是释放它  让它回宇宙\NYou are setting it free, sending it back to the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.88,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你是和平使者\NYou are the bringer of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你能感受到树的每个原子\NCan you feel every atom of the tree
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.53,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,拉扯着另一个原子\Npulling on every other atom,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:47.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,而世界上其它的原子\Nand all the other atoms in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.55,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,拉扯着那些原子吗\Npulling on those atoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:53.08,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这就是宇宙永恒的激烈竞争\NThat is the eternal tug-of-war of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:54.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我想让你\NI want you to take
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:57.13,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,使用不间断的静态力量\Nall that relentless static background power
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:05:58.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,逆转它\Nand reverse it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:03.04,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,将引力转换为推力\NTurn the pull into a push.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:09.55,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,使用你头脑中的光\NUse the light in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:39.62,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,天赋异禀\NSingularly gifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:41.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我没法呼吸了\NI can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:42.36,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,歇会儿吧\NRest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:45.76,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你的力量会回来的  而且更为强大\NYour strength will come back, stronger next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:57.67,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我能变得多强大\NHow strong can I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.53,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这取决于你在训练中有多刻苦\NIt depends on how disciplined you are in your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:02.75,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你的潜力无限\NYour potential is unlimited.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:04.67,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我能制造出星星吗\NCould I make a star?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:09.37,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你完善后的力量会是非凡的\NYour perfected power will be...divine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.23,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们从激光飞船内部收到了无线电广播\NWe received a radio transmission from inside the Beamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:23.10,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那是循环程序  一直在播那一段消息\NYeah, it was a loop -- the same message over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.10,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,"集中营被清空了\N"The ghettos are being emptied.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.99,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,安达卢西亚几乎无人幸存\NAlmost no one is left in Andalusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:32.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,意大利和摩洛哥也是如此\NIt is the same in Italy and Morocco.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:35.25,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,所有人都被送去转化了\NVirtually everyone has been taken for processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:39.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,敌人有了新武器  来捕捉人类逃亡者\NThe enemy has a new weapon to capture human fugitives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:42.66,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我见过  很恐怖\NI've seen it. It's horrific,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:45.38,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,比我们之前碰到的一切武器更强大\Nbeyond anything we have encountered before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:49.18,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,相信我  我们无力抵抗\NBelieve me when I say there is no defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:51.70,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,任何听到这条信息的人应该明白\NAnyone hearing this should realize
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:54.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你们是人类的最后幸存者\Nyou are one of the last remaining pockets of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:57.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不要试图反抗\NDo not attempt to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:59.09,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,转入地下\NGo to ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:00.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,撤退\NRetreat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.32,0:08:02.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,躲藏\Nhide...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:03.96,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,生存下去\Nsurvive...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.18,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不然这就是人类的末日"\NOr this is the end."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:11.66,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们怎么知道这是真的\NHow do we know this is real,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:13.60,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,而不是艾士芬尼的另一个圈套\Nnot just another Espheni trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:15.82,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不知道  这条消息是在\NWe don't. But it was broadcast on a frequency
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:16.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们的频率上进行广播的\Nthat we think was ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:18.01,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那是什么频率\NWhat frequency is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:21.76,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,1776兆赫  美国独立的年份\N1776 megahertz, as in American Independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:24.41,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,有人在找我们  希望我们收到消息\NSomebody's looking out for us, hoping we'd get the code.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.17,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那我们要怎么做\NSo, what are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.83,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那声音说我们需要撤退躲藏生存下去\NThose voices said we need to retreat, hide, survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:30.32,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,可我们没地方躲了\NWe're kind of running out of places to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:31.52,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,要离开这里吗\NWe just gonna leave here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:33.34,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是啊  我们要去解放其它集中营\NYeah, we're gonna go liberate another ghetto,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:34.77,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,把人们救出来  在...\Nget some people out of there before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,在什么之前\NBefore what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.16,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,艾士芬尼的方案正在进行中\NThe Espheni solution is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:39.45,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我亲眼所见\NI've seen it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:40.87,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这听起来像是另一个\NWell, it sounds like yet another
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:43.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,"守住阵地"的方法\N"hold down the fort" detail to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.07,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,而我个人绝对无意于\Nand I, for one, have no intention
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:48.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,再次坐以待毙\Nof playing the sitting-duck card again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:50.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,玛吉说得对\NMaggie's right, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:53.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,集合招募一些新人有什么不对\NWhat's wrong with rounding up some new recruits, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:55.37,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们壮大队伍  离开这里\NWe replenish the army, we get out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:57.53,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,干掉那些蟑螂\Nand we frag those cockroaches, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果那广播说的是真事\N'Cause if that broadcast is telling the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:01.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,转化进展到这种地步了\Nand this mutation process is that far along,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.40,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们必须更积极地应对\Nwe need to do something even more aggressive than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:05.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我忘了你的终极规划\NSorry, I forgot your master plan --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:07.29,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,要劫持外面的千年隼号\NHijack the, uh, Millennium Falcon out there
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.61,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,然后飞向月球\Nand fly it to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:10.32,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,珀普  闭嘴\NPope, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:12.95,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我还没听到更好的计划  至少你没说出来\NHaven't heard a better plan yet. Not out of you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:16.36,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们没法赢得消耗战  我们没有人手\NWe can't win a war of attrition. We don't have the numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:20.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们要进行的也许不是最理性的计划\NWhat we are about to embark on may not be the most rational plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:23.46,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但我相信这是最可能成功的计划\Nbut I do believe that it is the plan with the best chance of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:26.91,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果我们没时间了  也许这太绝望了\NIf we've run out of time, maybe this is too desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:28.59,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,也许我们该躲起来\NMaybe we should just hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就我个人而言  我不会躲起来\NOkay, I'm just gonna speak for myself. I'm not gonna hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:36.82,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我受够了四处觅食  行尸走肉一般活下去\NI'm sick of scrounging around and just surviving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:41.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我肯定我们能找到一个洞穴  可以维持\NI'm sure we could find a cave, and we could eke out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:42.27,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,一周  一个月或者一年\Nanother week or another month, another year,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:44.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但...  我更想赢得战争\Nbut that -- I want to win the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:48.67,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果有办法  如果有任何办法\NAnd if there's a way -- if there is any way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:51.46,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,削弱艾士芬尼的能量核\Nthat we can cripple the Espheni power core,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:53.91,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,打倒它们的战争防御\Nwe can bring down their war defenses,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:55.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我一定会照做\Nthen that's what I'm gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,汤姆说得对  这样活不下去\NTom's right. This is no way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:09.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你觉得谁会那么愚蠢\NAnd exactly who do you propose would be foolish enough
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:12.74,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,驾驶那个飞碟飞向月球\Nto pilot that flying saucer to the moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:14.94,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我\NMe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:22.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我觉得你太轻率了\NI just think you're being rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:24.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你在机械地应对局势\NYou're treating this situation by rote,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:25.50,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果这只是另一个...\Nif it's just another --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:26.35,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我没有机械应对\NThere's nothing rote about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:29.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是我在推动计划  我得付诸行动\NI'm the one driving the plan. I have to walk the walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:30.46,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你这样做\NAnd I'm glad you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:32.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-大家都是  -但是呢\N- Everyone is. - But?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但你不能再次做出单方决定\NBut you can't make another unilateral decision
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:35.88,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就因为这是两点之间最短的距离\Njust because it's the shortest distance between two points.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:37.31,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,根本没有好选择\NThere are no good options here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:39.36,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我知道  而且我明白你担心\NI mean, I see that, and I know that you're worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.72,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不仅仅是担心\NIt's more than that I'm just worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:44.09,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你要驾驶着外星人飞船飞向月球了  汤姆\NI mean, you are flying on an alien spaceship to the moon, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,想想吧\NA-and just think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:47.45,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你摧毁了能量核后\NOnce you destroy the power core,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.84,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那不就能毁灭一切艾士芬尼驱动的东西吗\Ndoesn't that kill everything Espheni-powered?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:52.25,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么回来呢\NHow the hell are you planning on getting back, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:54.17,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,科奇斯研究过了\NCochise has done his homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:57.39,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,他说激光飞船中应该储存有足够的能量\NHe says there should be enough stored power in the Beamer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:11:00.11,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,能飞回地球  像电池之类的东西\Nto fly it home, in a -- like, a battery or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:01.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那还真是令人欣慰啊\NOh. Well, that's -- that's reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:04.01,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好吧  一旦地球上的艾士芬尼\NOkay, well, once the Espheni here on earth
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:05.45,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,意识到自己惨遭重创\Nrealize that they've been hit hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:07.95,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你觉得它们不会报复吗\Nyou think they're not gonna retaliate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:09.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你不觉得它们报复的时候\NAnd don't you think we need you here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:10.95,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-我们需要你在这里吗  -这是两个人的工作\N- alive when they do? - It's a two-man job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:13.27,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,科奇斯驾驶  我来部署炸弹\NCochise pilots, and I have to deploy the bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:15.84,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但我没法让别人去做\NHey, but I can't ask somebody else to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.13,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我要身先士卒\NAnd I need to lead by example.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:20.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,可以  但先要得到你领导的人们的同意\NI want you to lead, but with the consent of those you're leading.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:22.37,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,汤姆  你得认真想想\NTom, you've got to think it through
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:24.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,让你身边的人和你一起想清楚\Nand allow the people around you to think it through with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:27.65,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们成功的唯一方法\NThat is the only way we pull this off --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:30.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就是大家一起做决定\Nif we decide things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:36.67,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我明白你的意思  真的\NI hear what you're saying, I really do,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:39.34,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我知道你说的不止是团队\Nand I know you're not just talking about the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:44.23,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们现在是搭档\NWe are -- we are partners now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-是啊  -你明白吗\N- Yeah. - You got me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:48.96,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我明白\NYeah, I got you. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:50.64,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.55,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,打扰了\NUh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:55.25,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没事  怎么了\NIt's okay. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:56.55,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们需要你来一下激光飞船\NWe need you at the beamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:01.72,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:06.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们正在干活儿  突然间\NWe were working, and all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:08.79,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,从激光飞船的控制台伸出了这些触须\Nthese tendrils lurched out of the beamer console
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:10.72,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,缠住了沃尔姆通讯器\Nand seized the Volm communicator.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:11.78,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,然后烧焦了它\NAnd fried it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:14.16,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这是因为我们在使用沃尔姆科技\NIt is because we integrated the Volm technology
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:16.46,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,来登录飞船的航行系统\Nin order to access the ship's navigation system.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:19.69,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,显然  激光飞船配备有防御机制\NApparently, this beamer is armed with a defense mechanism
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:21.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,发现了沃尔姆的覆盖命令\Nwhich recognized the Volm override.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:23.83,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我担心等飞船完全激活后\NOnce this ship is fully activated,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:26.64,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,发现任何沃尔姆的存在\NI worry it will recognize any Volm presence
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:27.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,也将会拒绝执行我的命令\Nand will reject me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.50,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你是说你不能参与这个任务了吗\NYou're saying you can't go on the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:31.65,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我是可以的  但是\NI could, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:34.49,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我的参加会导致计划失败\Nit would jeopardize our objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,所以我们之中的唯一一个\NSo, the only one of us who has any understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:38.62,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,了解这东西怎么运作的人不能参加\Nof how this thing works is grounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:42.02,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,看来这便车搭不成了\NSo much for hitching a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:47.31,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,还是有一个机会的\NThere is... one possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:52.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果能在人工操作下让它\NIf we can manage to fly this beamer manually
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:54.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,升出地球大气的干扰\Nabove the interference of Earth's atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:56.75,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,它有可能可以自动锁定\Nthere is a chance it will automatically lock onto
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:59.04,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,归航信标  返回艾士芬尼能量核\Nthe homing beacon to the Espheni power core.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-然后自动飞向月球  -是的\N- And then fly itself to the moon? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:04.83,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,所以它不是个魔毯  它是架飞机\NSo it's not a magic carpet, it's an airplane?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:07.89,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,飞机有四种基本操作\NAirplanes have four basic controls --
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:09.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,推力  俯仰  偏航  横滚\Nthrust, pitch, yaw, roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:12.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们已经会俯仰和偏航  多亏了你儿子\NAnd we already know pitch and yaw, thanks to your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:16.80,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,而且也知道控制面板在哪儿  多亏了你儿子\NAnd we know where the main control panel is, thanks to your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:21.48,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,现在我们只需找到控制推力和横滚的方法了\NSo, then, all we need to isolate is thrust and roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:23.29,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就用老办法来吧\Nthe old-fashioned way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:27.65,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,开始\NPull!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:29.43,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没反应\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:33.29,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,开始\NPull!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:34.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没反应\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:37.29,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,开始\NPull!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:41.88,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,停下  停下\NStop! stop! stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:46.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,科奇斯差点就被吸入进气道了\NCochise nearly got sucked through the intake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:48.42,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,推力找到了\NThrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:51.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,开始\NPull.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:13:59.85,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,炸弹做的怎么样了\NHow's the bomb coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:06.04,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我说  炸弹做的怎么样了\NI said, um, how's the bomb coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:09.63,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果没办法控制催化剂\NWell, if we can't figure out a way to control this accelerant,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就很难把握爆炸的时机\Nit's gonna be hard to time the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:15.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我...\NLook, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:19.61,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我知道我越界了\NI know I crossed the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:21.49,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,什么界啊\NAnd what line is that --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:22.43,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,追你哥哥的女友时\Nthe line you don't cross
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:25.30,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,还有什么界限可言吗\Nwhen you're hitting on your brother's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:29.64,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你要理解  我们没法控制此事\NYou have to understand, it -- we couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:32.25,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这是刺钉的作用\NS-something's going on with the spikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:33.79,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,原来是刺钉啊  好吧\NSpikes. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道不是因为你就是爱上了她\NHow do you know you don't just like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:39.59,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我和玛吉本来不会有任何关系  要不是...\NI wouldn't have done anything with Maggie if it wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:41.19,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你是我哥哥  哈尔\NYou're my brother, Hal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:43.43,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我绝不会有意伤害你\NI'd n-never do anything to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:48.16,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,说得容易\NThat's easy to say, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:02.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们还没找到横滚的机制  但一定能的\NWe haven't isolated the roll mechanism just yet, but we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:04.36,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,可能性太多了\NThere are so many options.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:05.87,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,什么时候能试飞呢\NWhen can we take it for a test drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.92,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不知道试飞能不能直接就...\NI doubt we'll be able to take it for a test drive before --
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:10.40,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,可我们并不是要精准的降落在航空母舰上\NWell, remember, we don't have to land on a navy carrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:12.72,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们要做的只是让它升空\NI mean, all we have to do is fly up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:14.94,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,可以说目标就是天空\NThe sky is literally the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:16.67,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,根据科奇斯的判断结论\NAccording to Cochise's diagnostics,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:17.84,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,一旦进入太空\Nonce in space,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:20.34,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,激光飞船就能锁定艾士芬尼归航信标\Nthe beamer will lock onto the Espheni homing beacon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,自动飞向月球基地\Nand fly to the moon base on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.71,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但我们还是得做些基本训练\NWe still need to train with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:25.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,至少需要两个人丢炸弹\NI mean, it's gonna take two people to drop the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:26.10,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我来驾驶  然后...\NI can pilot it --
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:28.36,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,等等  这事还没定吧  伙计\NWhoa. Uh, has that been decided yet, partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:30.52,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,当然定了  他一直都爱抢功\NOf course it has. He's a glory hog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:33.31,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,等等  我想重点不在于功劳吧\NHold on. I realize it's not about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:34.50,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但是汤姆\NBut, Tom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:37.68,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,至少这个任务是独一无二的\Nthis task is unique, to say the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:41.07,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这并不是一次救援或者夺取武器的任务\NIt's not just another rescue mission or weapons grab.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:42.85,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这事是要永载史册的\NThis is for all the marbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:44.35,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不应该至少\NShouldn't there be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:47.41,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,有个更公平的决策过程吗\Na fair process to determine how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:48.19,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,听起来不错\NSounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.10,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我同意\NI agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:53.42,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们应该抽签以示公平\NWe should draw straws to be fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.25,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这话居然是个孩子说的\NOut of the mouths of babes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:56.83,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,而且我觉得不错\NSounds like a good idea to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.45,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,抽签  开玩笑吗\NDraw straws? Are you joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:02.08,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这不是游戏\NThis isn't a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.70,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们要的是合适的人选\NWe should pick the right person for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:06.85,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那谁说你就是那个合适人选了呢\NExactly who said that you were the best person for the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:11.75,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我有13小时的飞行经历  你有吗\NI have 13 registered hours as a pilot. Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.49,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-我喜欢这个方法  -听起来不错\N- I like it. - Sounds pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:14.65,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-我也想试试  -你有...\N- I want to take a shot. - You got something --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:15.63,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-嘿  -我也想干这事\N- Hey... - I want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:18.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我觉得这事不能凭运气决定\NI don't think any of this should be left to chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:20.10,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那你可以反对抽签\NThen you can vote against the draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:21.63,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,同意的举手\NWho's for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:34.94,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好吧  我们抽签\NOkay, we'll draw straws.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:37.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这是个很危险的任务\NIt's a very dangerous mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:39.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,谁也不能被迫参加  报名必须是自愿的\NNobody should be forced to go. Draw should be voluntary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:41.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我要说一句  大家都要\NI tell you what -- think very carefully
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:43.49,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,谨慎考虑要不要自愿报名\Nwhether or not you want to volunteer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:47.95,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果愿意  待会儿再回来\NIf you do come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:50.48,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们会在这儿放纸笔\NWe'll get pen, paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:53.62,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,写下你的名字  放进来  晚上再开会\NWrite your names out. Put them in here. Come back tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:56.26,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,然后我们抽签 看看谁是这个幸运儿\NWe'll pull out the names, find out who got lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.54,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-我为你骄傲  -骄傲什么\N- I'm proud of you. - For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:16.69,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,骄傲你同意抽签  这是个很民主的决定\NFor going with the draw. It was very democratic of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:18.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,也调动了很大的积极性\NI also think it got everyone more invested.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:20.02,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我已经报名了\NI already put my name in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:26.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我觉得这是个糟糕透顶的办法\NI think it's a horrible idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:28.18,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们应该\NI think we should go with the person
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:30.48,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-让最有可能成功的人去  -是你\N- who's got the most chance of success... - Meaning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:31.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,而不是随机挑选出来的人\N... not just pick people at random.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:35.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,顺便问句  如果哈尔或本被选中怎么办\NBy the way, what happens if Hal or Ben gets picked?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:37.54,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我会郁闷  但我们不能随便破例\NI would hate that, but we can't make exceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:38.88,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-就因为...  -因为他们是我的孩子吗\N- just because... - Because they're my children?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:40.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们难道不是一家人吗\NAren't we all a family now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.09,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是  很抱歉我说了这样的话\NYeah. I'm sorry I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:49.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不过结果如何你不能反悔吧\NLook, you're gonna accept the results, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:51.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你不能用你的权力改变人选吧\NYou're not gonna pull rank if you don't like who gets decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:53.49,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我真的不知道如果被选中的人\NI honestly don't know how I would react
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是我的儿子我会作何反应\Nif one of the boys gets picked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.02,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我和你一样\NI'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:58.70,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不是只有你能拯救世界  汤姆\NYou're not the only one who can save the world, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:00.49,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我想报名\NI want to put my name in the draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:03.72,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不行  你才13岁\NNo. You're 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.26,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你说过圣女贞德想要为她的国家而战时\NYou said Joan of Arc was a teenager when
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:06.13,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,也才十几岁而已\Nshe wanted to fight for her country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:08.35,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-别跟我贫嘴  -抽签还是我的意见呢\N- Don't get smart with me right now, please. - The draw was my idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:10.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我知道  但是15岁以上\NYeah, I know, but you have to be 15
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:11.26,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,才能驾驶外星飞船\Nto pilot an alien spaceship,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:12.60,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你连驾照都没有呢\Nand you don't have your learner's permit yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-真是的  -没什么好说的了\N- God! - End of discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:20.82,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我很担心这孩子呢\NWorried about that kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:40.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你想谈谈混血的事吗  兄弟\NYou wanted to discuss the hybrid, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:43.61,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我担心不久你就无法掌控她了\NI'm worried you won't be able to control her for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:47.26,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不用担心  她完全效忠于我们\NDon't be. She's completey committed to our cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:49.44,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,她完全效忠于我们\NShe's completely committed to our cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:06.37,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,她更趋近于人类而不是艾士芬尼\NShe's more human than Espheni.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:10.27,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,她认为人类是低级物种  像我们教的那样\NShe sees humanity as inferio, as she has been taught.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:12.48,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你也看见了她对那棵树所做的事\NYou saw what she did to the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:14.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,正是因为那件事我才召唤你\NThat's the reason I summoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:16.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,她的进步之快\NShe's progressing much more quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,超乎我的想象\Nthan I could've imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:20.95,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,凭她一己之力就能帮我们赢得战争\NShe could single-handedy win us the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:23.09,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但如果她背叛  我们就会输\NOr lose it if she rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.10,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,她不会背叛的\NShe's not going to rebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.99,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,而且就算她背叛了\NAnd even if she did,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:29.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我还有特殊的方法控制她\NI have a special means to control her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:32.92,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,相信我  她不知道我们要用她干什么\NTrust me -- she has no idea of our purpose for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:36.10,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,她以为她的能力是以带来和平为目的\NShe thinks her power is being developed for peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:37.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不在乎  结束它\NI don't care. End it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:41.38,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我要你消除她所带来的隐患\NI want you to eliminate the risk she represents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:43.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你想要我杀了她吗\NYou want me to kill she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:48.02,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这是最保险的方式\NThat's the safest course of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:50.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,按我说的去做  结束她\NNow do as I say. End her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.09,0:19:53.59,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好的  兄弟\NYes, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:24.70,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我报名时看见你也把名字放进去了\NI saw you put your name in the draw when I put mine in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:26.69,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这是最好的决定\NIt's the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:29.71,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你什么意思\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:31.31,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,字面意思\NJust that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:33.77,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我想做正确的事...\NI try to do the right thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,为了我的家人...\Nfor my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:38.96,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,和我爱的人\Nthe people I care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:41.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我也是\NSo do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:44.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我看见你和本的事了\NI saw you with Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:47.37,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,对不起  哈尔\NI'm so sorry, Hal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:49.48,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这...\NIt's --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:53.74,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,本和我因为刺钉联系在了一起\NBen and I have this connection because of the spikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:57.04,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这完全是生理反应  我...\NIt's more physical than anything else. I --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:00.63,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么解释\NI don't know how to explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:03.41,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我已经知道了\NYou know, I've already heard this story, and, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.78,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,而且我也理解\NYou know what? I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:07.60,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,也许你们俩是天生一对\NYou know, maybe the two of you are meant for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:10.31,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不  我不是这个意思\NNo. That's not what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,当我和本距离很近时\NWhen Ben and I are near each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:15.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就有一种像是被刺钉链接起来了的感觉\Nit's like the spikes are attracted to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:17.76,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这不是我们能控制的\NIt's totally out of our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:19.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你们俩可以把\NYou know, it's just so convenient
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:20.99,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没有自控力的责任推卸给刺钉\Nthat you both have these spikes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:22.78,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,真是方便极了\Nthat you can blame for your lack of self-control.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:24.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,也许你还不知道\NI got news for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:26.94,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但每个人都对刺钉有自己的看法\NEverybody's got their version of spikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.72,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我的看法是  这叫心心相惜\N"Heart wants what it wants."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:31.36,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,可我并不想和本在一起\NI don't want to be with Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:33.49,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这才是我想说的\NThat's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:39.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  事实是...\NYou know, the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:43.38,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你伤害了我\Nyou just really hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:07.82,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你在干什么\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:11.29,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我早该知道的\NI should've known you --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:13.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你反悔了\Nyou'd try to get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.24,0:22:17.35,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,放了名字然后溜回来想取出来  对吗\NPut your name in and sneak back and take it out, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.07,0:22:19.83,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你知道你这种人叫什么吗\NThere's a word for people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:22.76,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,什么啊  懦夫吗\NYeah, what's that? Coward?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:27.26,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,拜托  提出我们应该站起来\NPlease. I'm the one saying we should get off our ass,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:28.80,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,召集人们拿上武器\Nround up some men and some weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:30.68,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,去屠杀这些外星害虫的人就是我\Nand frag these cockroaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.89,0:22:32.62,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那就别抱怨去做事\NYeah, why don't you quit complaining and go do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.63,0:22:35.46,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我也想  但我一个人做不到\NI would. But I can't -- not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.17,0:22:38.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,梅森给大家都洗脑了\NMason's got everybody so brainwashed --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.01,0:22:39.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是这样啊\NIs that what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:41.63,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你总是有各种借口  珀普\NYou never run out of excuses, do you, Pope?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.64,0:22:43.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,怎么  就因为我不想\NWhy, because I don't see the point
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:46.46,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,浪费时间在毫无希望的赌局上吗\Nin wasting nothing but time on a wing and a prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:49.17,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就算他们真能启动那个激光飞船\NYou know, even if they get that beamer running,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:50.74,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,它也一定会坠毁\Nit's gonna crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.46,0:22:54.83,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,与此同时  我们这些剩下的人\NMeanwhile, the rest of us -- see, we're all sitting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.84,0:22:58.35,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,还无所事事的坐在这里成为靶子\Nin one place with a giant target on our heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:01.48,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,走着瞧吧\NYou watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.64,0:23:04.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这个小冒险\NThis little "adventure,"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.68,0:23:06.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,会和所有冒险一个下场\Nit's gonna end like they all end --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:09.94,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那就是失败\Nwith a smudge on a windshield.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.37,0:23:13.52,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们不过是小白鼠  上尉  在等着\NWe're all just a bunch of lab rats, Cap, just waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:16.07,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,看它们下次又能想出什么样的\Nfor whatever delightful little Skitter experiment
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:17.67,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,迅猎兽实验\Nthey're brewing up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:21.74,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不过  你应该早就懂了的吧\NThen again, you'd probably know all about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.74,0:23:22.59,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不是吗\Nnow, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.13,0:23:48.40,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我没有把我的名签从颅骨里拿出来\NI didn't take my name out of the skull!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.84,0:23:51.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我没有把我的名签从颅骨里拿出来\NI didn't take my name out of the skull.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.35,0:23:53.89,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我亲眼看见你这么干了\NI just saw you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.97,0:23:56.88,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我拿的不是我的  是你的\NIt wasn't my name. It was yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:23:59.47,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你和梅森的\Nyours and Mason's.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:00.50,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.42,0:24:03.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你说什么呢\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.08,0:24:05.02,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,给我拿来\NGive me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.30,0:24:08.15,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我要开那艘飞船\NI need to be on that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.06,0:24:11.76,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,行了吧  我想被选中\NAll right? I need to be chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:14.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,听着\NLook --
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.71,0:24:16.99,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这些人\Nthese people, they...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.49,0:24:19.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,他们需要你\Nthey need you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.94,0:24:22.87,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,需要你和梅森  没人需要我\Nyou and Mason. Nobody needs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.18,0:24:26.40,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果我明天失踪了\NI could disappear tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.40,0:24:28.26,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,可能都没人会注意到\NI really doubt that anybody's gonna notice, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.27,0:24:30.04,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我一定要上那艘激光飞船上\NI got to be on that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.56,0:24:32.25,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,它是有去无回的  对吧\NThat Beamer's on a one-way ticket, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.26,0:24:34.65,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,它不会回来了  我们都知道\NIt ain't coming back, and we both know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.08,0:24:36.98,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,让我...\NLet me be...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.04,0:24:39.82,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,让我来做这个英雄吧  丹\Nlet me be the hero, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.84,0:24:42.47,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,让我来做殉道者\NLet me be the martyr.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.68,0:24:44.48,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好吗\NRight?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.43,0:24:48.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这次任务  能够造福全人类\NThe mission's just -- just a Hail-Mary for the planet, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.60,0:24:49.63,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,让我...\NLet me do...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.95,0:24:52.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,做点...做点...\Nsomething -- something --
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.85,0:24:54.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,能流芳百世的事吧\Nsomething worth remembering.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.26,0:24:57.02,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你是说  这对你来说\NSo you're saying that, for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.37,0:24:59.15,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是一种解脱\Nthis is just another way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.50,0:25:04.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果是呢\NSo what if it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.20,0:25:06.94,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你是认真的吗  珀普\NAre you serious, Pope?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.06,0:25:09.50,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不想继续了  不想战斗  不想逃跑\NI'm done. I'm done fighting. I'm done running.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.66,0:25:11.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我什么都不想干了\NI'm done with the whole program.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.10,0:25:15.04,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,梅森在这件事上是对的\NMason's right about one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.67,0:25:16.59,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们...\NThis is...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.23,0:25:20.09,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们活不下去  也不值得活下去了\Nthis is no way to live. This life is not worth living.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.94,0:25:22.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,况且我有什么\NAnd what do I got?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.43,0:25:24.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没有家人  没有...\NI got no family. I got...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.05,0:25:28.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,没有老婆孩子\NI got no kids, no wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.64,0:25:29.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,一无所有\NI got nothing, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.76,0:25:33.45,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,她可能会回来的\NShe might come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.04,0:25:43.95,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,起来吧\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.53,0:25:45.67,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,很抱歉\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.28,0:25:48.27,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我承认错误\NI-I stand corrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.57,0:25:49.62,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我以为...\NI thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.26,0:25:51.44,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我知道你是怎么想的\NI know what you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.34,0:26:08.31,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,能让我来吗\NMind if I do the honors?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.57,0:26:10.35,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,请吧\NGo ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.16,0:26:14.42,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这里有很多名字\NLot of names in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.04,0:26:16.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,天哪  有谁没把自己的名字放进去吗\NBoy, did anybody not put their name?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.06,0:26:20.16,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,意义很大\NThat says a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.12,0:26:22.26,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.39,0:26:27.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好了\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.76,0:26:30.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,被选中的是...\NThe winner is...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.78,0:26:42.36,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,本\NBen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.63,0:26:44.69,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,加油  孩子\NWay to go, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.75,0:26:46.64,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-我支持你  孩子  -加油  本\N- I got your back, kid. - Way to go, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.48,0:27:03.86,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这是一个\NWell, that's one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.37,0:27:05.60,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,另一个是谁\NWho's the other?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.23,0:27:25.08,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是我\NIt's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.25,0:27:31.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我能看看吗\NMay I?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.56,0:27:36.80,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,看来是我俩了  我们能成功\NLooks like it's you and me. We got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.89,0:27:38.71,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是的  我们能成功\NYeah, we got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.93,0:27:48.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,费了这么大劲  还是他被选中了\NWell, after all of that... he gets picked anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.16,0:27:49.31,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,真是经典\NNow, that is classic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.15,0:27:51.64,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,一家人中选中了两个\NTwo from one family.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.67,0:27:55.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,事已至此\NThat's the way the cookie crumbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.05,0:28:14.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,在出发之前我有很多事要做  所以...\NI got a lot to do before I go, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.51,0:28:16.08,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,汤姆\NTom...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.87,0:28:18.10,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你能先坐下吗\Nwill you sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.45,0:28:20.39,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,拜托\NPlease?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.43,0:28:27.83,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你有没有那么做\NDid you or didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.45,0:28:29.87,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,有没有做什么\NDid I or didn't I what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.16,0:28:31.32,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,作弊\NFix the draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.30,0:28:37.41,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这可能是我们最后一次在一起\NThis might be the last time we're together.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.60,0:28:39.32,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你就想这么离开我们吗\NIs this really how you want to leave us?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.03,0:28:43.44,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-你是不是把它放在手中  -是的\N- Did you palm it? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.83,0:28:45.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我作弊了\NI fixed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.14,0:28:50.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你是懂历史的\NYou know history.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.22,0:28:54.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这就是那种导致失败的狂妄自大\NThis is exactly the kind of hubris that comes before the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.25,0:28:56.40,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,如果被人发现了\NIf people found out,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.59,0:28:58.83,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,会毁掉人们对你作为领袖的信任\Nit would destroy their trust in your leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.15,0:29:01.99,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,会毁掉一切我们为之抗争的事\NIt would jeopardize everything we've been fighting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.05,0:29:06.82,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你真的愿意冒这么大的风险吗\NAre you really willing to risk all of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.88,0:29:08.83,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不会让本自己去的\NI'm not willing to let Ben go without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.57,0:29:14.38,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但不仅仅是因为这个  我有种感觉\NBut even more than that, I just have this feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.40,0:29:16.15,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就好像我应该参加这次任务似的\Nlike I'm supposed to go on this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.35,0:29:22.37,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我想不出该怎么描述这种感觉\NI can't even think of any other way to describe it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.37,0:29:24.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,反正我就是这么觉得\Nexcept I just have this sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.72,0:29:27.35,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这就是我应该做的\NThis is what I'm supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.24,0:29:32.94,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,就像你对亚蕾克西的信念一样\NIt's like your belief in Lexi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.87,0:29:50.39,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,准备好训练了吗\NAre you ready to train?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.58,0:29:51.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是的  父亲\NYes, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.19,0:29:54.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,闭上你的眼睛\NClose your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.14,0:29:56.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,放松\NRelax.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.56,0:29:58.48,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-用...  -我心中的光\N- Use the... - The light in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.74,0:30:00.70,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是的  没错\NYes. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.09,0:30:22.53,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我一直在练习\NI've been practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.29,0:30:24.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,别害怕\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.20,0:30:27.09,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我是带来和平的人  还记得吧\NI'm the bringer of peace, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.26,0:30:31.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我听到了你们兄弟在阴影位面的对话\NI heard your conversation with your brother in the shadow plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.66,0:30:33.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我带来的根本不是和平\NI'm not the bringer of peace at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.99,0:30:35.35,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,而是死亡\NI'm the bringer of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.39,0:30:39.84,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,有一件事你说对了\NYou were right about one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.32,0:30:42.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,完善后的能力是非凡的\NPower perfected is divine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.86,0:31:01.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,说实话\NGot to be honest --
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.34,0:31:02.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我希望是我跟你一起去\NI wish I was the one going up there with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.01,0:31:09.69,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,据说在月球上能把高尔夫球打出两英里外\NThey say you can hit a golf ball about two miles up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.62,0:31:13.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,可是球进洞一定很难\NBet the putting's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.64,0:31:19.17,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,要开激光飞船了  你有什么感觉\NHow do you feel about flying the Beamer?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.84,0:31:21.37,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,基本的控制我都会了\NI got the basic controls down,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.38,0:31:23.28,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但在我们真正地出发之前\Nbut until we go live, until we do it for real...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.77,0:31:26.04,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我也不确定\Nwell, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.21,0:31:28.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-只有做了才知道  -没错\N- Nothing to it but to do it. - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.66,0:31:32.69,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我听说了你和本的事\NSo, I heard about you and Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.19,0:31:35.47,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是吗  谁告诉你的\NYeah? Who told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.27,0:31:37.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,本\NBen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.97,0:31:40.64,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,他说如果不是因为刺钉的话\NHe said none of this would've happened
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.66,0:31:42.02,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这一切都不会发生\Nif it hadn't been for the spikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.91,0:31:44.62,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这就像说  如果不是因为艾士芬尼的话\NYou know, that's like saying the war wouldn't have happened
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.64,0:31:45.46,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这场战争就不会发生\Nif it wasn't for the Espheni.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.47,0:31:47.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不知道是不是跟刺钉有关\NI don't know if it had anything to do with the spikes or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.37,0:31:50.50,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但我了解本  我了解他的性格\NI do know Ben. I do know his character.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.65,0:31:54.99,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,玛吉跟我说他们对彼此都有感觉\NMaggie told me they both got feelings for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.44,0:31:57.38,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,很遗憾\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.68,0:32:04.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,在历史上  这也不是第一次\NYou're not the first brothers in history
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.01,0:32:05.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,兄弟俩喜欢上同一个女孩了\Nto fall for the same girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.51,0:32:08.70,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,而且  最终也不是由你或本来决定\NAnd ultimately, it won't be up to you or Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.73,0:32:09.63,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,还是要由玛吉来决定\NIt'll be up to Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.04,0:32:14.61,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,一开始是我坚持要给她移植刺钉的\NI'm the one who pushed to give her those spikes in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.51,0:32:17.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,他想见你\NHe wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.82,0:32:20.65,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你应该去看看你弟弟\NYou should go see your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.57,0:32:25.71,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-这可能是最后的机会了  -别这么说\N- You might not get another chance. - Don't talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.76,0:32:27.87,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,别让我这样说\NWell, hey, don't make me feel like I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.54,0:32:49.42,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我很害怕\NThis one has me scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.56,0:32:55.21,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我应该一开始就向你坦白\NI should've told you everything from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.52,0:32:58.99,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,很抱歉我没有那么做  不会再有下次了\NI'm sorry that I didn't. It won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.38,0:33:04.19,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,但你对作弊的事不后悔  是吧\NBut you're not sorry you fixed the draw, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.97,0:33:06.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是的\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.46,0:33:10.59,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我不会说出去\NI won't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.90,0:33:13.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我应该想得到\NI should've known...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.16,0:33:15.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,当他们说要抽签的时候\Nwhen they announced the draw,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.34,0:33:16.76,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你就能想出应对的办法\Nyou'd find a way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.70,0:33:22.22,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你是个好父亲\NYou're a good father.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.18,0:33:33.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我会尽一切努力回来找你\NI'm gonna do everything that I can to come back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.77,0:33:36.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我保证\NI promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.93,0:33:42.51,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我有一个礼物要给你\NI have a gift for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.43,0:33:46.17,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,离别礼物\NA going-away present?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.18,0:33:49.87,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,不  是结婚纪念日第二天礼物\NNope. A second-day anniversary present.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.87,0:33:51.16,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,是什么\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.56,0:34:01.63,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,斯多葛学派哲学家爱比克泰德的书\NEpictetus. The Stoic.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.35,0:34:06.19,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,《一个人应该为自己做好充分的准备》\N"A man should be prepared to be sufficient unto himself."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.65,0:34:09.69,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-这是我最喜欢的书之一  -我知道\N- It's one of my favorites. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.73,0:34:10.75,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你在哪儿发现的\NWhere'd you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.77,0:34:13.04,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,在我们找你的时候  在一堆乱石中发现的\NI found it in some rubble when we were digging for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.09,0:34:14.75,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,被我注意到了  我就留着了\NCaught my eye. I've been saving it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.80,0:34:15.59,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.84,0:34:19.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,能装进口袋里  很适合要出门的人\NIt's pocket-sized. It's perfect for the man on the go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.30,0:34:24.95,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你确定人要充分准备好吗\NYou sure a man should be sufficient unto himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.97,0:34:32.53,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,爱比克泰德知道什么\NWhat does Epictetus know?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.01,0:34:54.04,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,怎么样了\NHow's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.63,0:34:57.56,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,炸弹已经装好了\NBomb's packed,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.66,0:35:00.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,炸药在充电  检查了两遍导线\NSet the tovex for the charge, double-checked the wiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.61,0:35:02.80,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,连上计时器就行\NJust got to connect the timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.97,0:35:04.16,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我是说你\NI meant with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.87,0:35:07.68,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你一定很害怕  对吧\NI mean, you must be scared, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.39,0:35:13.08,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-我或许不应该来这  -或许吧\N- I probably shouldn't be here. - Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.03,0:35:17.90,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我是想来道别\NI just had to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.33,0:35:25.97,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我会想你的\NI'm gonna miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.53,0:35:29.13,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我  我不会去太长时间\NI'm-- I won't be gone too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.17,0:35:30.35,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,很快就回来了\NI'll be back before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.59,0:35:31.68,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我是认真的\NI'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.99,0:35:51.63,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我也会想你\NI'm gonna miss you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.01,0:36:12.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们不应该\NWe shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.25,0:36:15.49,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,哈尔\NHal.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.28,0:36:17.03,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,哈尔\NHal...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.77,0:36:28.30,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我是来接受你的道歉的\NI came to accept your apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.28,0:36:32.95,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-哈尔  -行了\N- Hal... - Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.02,0:36:35.30,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,别说了\Njust stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.60,0:36:38.51,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.82,0:36:45.94,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,哈尔\NHal!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.83,0:36:51.01,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,哈尔\NHal!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.62,0:37:03.49,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,最糟糕的道别\NWorst goodbye ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.21,0:37:12.13,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,好了  丁甘  我们应该都准备好了\NOkay, Dingaan. Looks like we're all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.53,0:37:14.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,对我们的飞行计划还有什么要说的吗\NAny last thoughts on our flight plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.61,0:37:16.61,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,记住  一旦进入高空大气\NRemember, once you reach the upper atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.62,0:37:18.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你们就会知道  因为那时就能看到日冕了\Nyou'll know it because you'll be able to see the corona.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.34,0:37:19.33,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,在北面\NAbove the surface to the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.36,0:37:20.66,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,那时我就应该打开信标\NThat's when I turn the beacon on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.70,0:37:21.34,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你已经知道了\NYou have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.40,0:37:22.82,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,谢谢你所做的一切  我的朋友\NThanks for everything, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.54,0:37:25.14,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-祝你好运  汤姆  -谢谢\N- Good luck, Tom. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.05,0:37:31.09,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,保护好我的家人\NKeep my family safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.57,0:37:33.36,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,一定  祝你成功\NYou got it. Godspeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.85,0:37:39.82,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,帮我照顾好韦弗上校  好吗\NKeep an eye on Colonel Weaver for me, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.85,0:37:42.00,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你在哪儿  哈尔\NWhere are you, Hal?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.80,0:37:46.45,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,马特  你要坚强\NMatt, I'm counting on you to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.20,0:37:49.31,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,别害怕自己的情绪波动\NDon't be afraid to let yourself feel things.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.58,0:37:52.50,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,知道  只是要坚强地克服它们\NI feel things. Just got to be tough about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.82,0:37:55.85,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-你也不必总是坚强  -不  我要\N- Well, you don't have to be so tough all the time. - Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.18,0:38:02.99,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,老爸  我爱你\NDad, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.46,0:38:07.57,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我也爱你\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.73,0:38:23.18,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\NThank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.10,0:38:27.52,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,保护了我\Nfor protecting me and for...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.94,0:38:30.17,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,爱我\Nloving me and...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.18,0:38:31.58,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,理解我\Nunderstanding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.80,0:38:36.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我会回来的\NI shall return.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.39,0:38:38.96,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你当然要回来  你还欠我一次蜜月\NOh, you better. You owe me a honeymoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.74,0:38:57.52,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我一直在想\NYou know, I was thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.54,0:38:58.93,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,昨晚发生的一切\Nabout everything that happened last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.96,0:39:03.03,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我只是想告诉你  我原谅你了\NAnd, I just want to let you know I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.77,0:39:11.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我的确对玛吉有感觉\NI do have feelings for Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.24,0:39:12.70,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,抱歉  但我真的有\NI'm sorry, but I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.88,0:39:18.36,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的坦白\NWell, thank you for coming clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.40,0:39:20.16,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,别担心  她是因为刺钉的关系\NDon't worry. For her, it's about the spikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.17,0:39:22.74,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我们还是别说这事了\NLet's just not even talk about it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.76,0:39:24.53,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,我觉得此时此刻不应该...\NI don't think this is the time or the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.48,0:39:30.10,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,谢谢你原谅我\NThanks for fogiving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.49,0:39:32.18,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,也谢谢你没有揍我\NAnd for not punching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.03,0:39:38.81,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,事实是  我不能决定玛吉该做什么\NYou know, the truth of matter is I am not the one to tell Maggie what she can
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.84,0:39:40.45,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,或者不该做什么  所以...\Nor can't do, anyway, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.96,0:39:42.38,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,这取决于她\Nit's up to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.79,0:39:46.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你说得对  这取决于她\NYou're right. It's up to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.58,0:39:49.30,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢  再过几年\NWho knows, man? Next couple of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.32,0:39:50.95,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,说不定是马特娶了她\NMatt will probably end up marrying her, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.42,0:39:54.06,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,来吧\NCome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.20,0:40:03.12,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,照顾好老爸  知道吗\NHey, keep an eye on dad up there, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.14,0:40:05.20,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-好的  -太好了\N- Yeah. - Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.18,0:40:08.09,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,很高兴看到你们和好了\NI'm glad to see you two made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.13,0:40:22.96,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,一定要成功\NGo get 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.04,0:40:25.96,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,等一下  等一下  别发射  停下\NWait! Wait! Stop the launch! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.99,0:40:27.24,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-怎么了  -我听到点东西\N- What's the matter? - I hear something!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.28,0:40:29.73,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-是什么  -有东西来了\N- The hell is it? - Something's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.65,0:40:33.84,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,快点  走  走\NCome on! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.50,0:40:46.52,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,激光飞船\NBeamers!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.89,0:40:49.08,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,找掩护\NTake cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.99,0:40:51.95,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,散开  散开  大家退后\NSpread out! Spread out! Everybody, back!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.45,0:40:54.40,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,退后  马特\NStand down, Matt!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.66,0:40:55.84,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,把枪放下\NPut that gun down.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.01,0:40:58.10,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,蹲下\NStay down!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.99,0:41:01.01,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,蹲下\NGet down.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.57,0:41:11.70,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,小心  马特\NLook out, Matt!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.20,0:41:26.61,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-怎么回事  -安全了\N- What happened?! - All clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.64,0:41:28.05,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,-它们在半空爆炸了  -什么\N- They just blew up in midair. - What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.37,0:41:29.54,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,谁干的\NWho did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.23,0:41:40.34,KaiTi yellow,,0,0,0,,你好  父亲\NHello, father.
